channel.title: Trying to set up a 614 server
channel.description:
I am trying to set up a 614 server and I've port forwarded the ports 43594 and 43595 or w.e they are, then I run the source and open the client and that's it lol I cant actually get in game. I'm using the source/client from http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=452322.0 and I havent edited anything Idk if i need to change some settings or something cause I just run the source and client and they are the same way they were when I downloaded them.
Anyone got like a brief tutorial via text how to set one up easily? Ive got no-ip and port forwarded and shit i just need to know what to do with the source and shit or if I should use a different source and client, Ive watched a couple videos and they sucked. Thanks.
